{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":603500,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"把手链看成手指了，吓了我一跳","timestamp":1606132388,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603512,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"李兆基自己焊接吧","timestamp":1606132565,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603524,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"呜呜呜求答案！是对我来说很重要的手链！（我反思……）","timestamp":1606132716,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603525,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"外面首饰店基本上都带服务的吧，最好是找原厂帮你修啊。","timestamp":1606132736,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603527,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 我……四体不勤五谷不分，并没有这个技能，但是感谢回答！","timestamp":1606132750,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603528,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"首选是原厂送修","timestamp":1606132754,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603531,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 是淘宝网购的……不过确实可以问问售后，谢谢","timestamp":1606132783,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603554,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"先提前感谢帮忙解答的dy们，顺便给大家分享个dz前两天发现的，不靠别人帮忙戴手链的方法，或许能帮到一些小姐姐（或小哥哥？）。一般戴不上是因为手链需要被扣上的那一头容易从手腕上滑下去，所以只要用一根皮筋或别的什么东西缠在手腕上把它固定住就行，但是这样扣好之后，皮筋可能会被扣在手链里面，所以可以选择那种用着不心疼的一次性小皮筋，扣好后直接剪断或者扯断，也可以选择那种可以再解开的绳子等等，总之就是找一个能解开的东西帮你固定没扣好的手链就好！","timestamp":1606133111,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603572,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"可以找那种带开口的小圆环两边一串就接起来了，就是外观会多个环... ","timestamp":1606133403,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":603596,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":125261,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 嗯，我也有在考虑这个方案，因为手链上原本也有不止一个环，所以我觉得外观上应该还好，准备自己试一试，感谢Dave！","timestamp":1606133650,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":125261,"reply":10,"tag":null,"text":"手链不小心扯断了（很细的那种一环一环的金属链子），校内外有什么地方能修吗，或者有什么能自己补救的方法吗","timestamp":1606131448,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}